    "editor": "code",
    "content": "The private gala celebrating the opening of the @[Eye of Anub-Ka](item:5594fa45-5159-41d5-b743-2a982466c629) exhibition begins at 6 p.m., and the @[Bureau of Civic Relics](landmark:399d89f1-c3cf-43f0-832a-2f3890b9f2f8) closes at 8 p.m. There's enough time for characters to prepare before attending, including retrieving or procuring formal attire if they don't wish to wear the clothes @[Samira Ament](person:4f7ec176-469e-498e-b19f-19b5d39c1bb1) provided. Weapons and visible armour are not permitted inside the museum and must be stashed in @[Samira Ament's](person:4f7ec176-469e-498e-b19f-19b5d39c1bb1) [i]bag of holding[/i] or elsewhere.\r\n\r\nOnce the characters are ready to enter the Bureau, keep track of which character has the [i]bag of holding[/i] that contains the group's adventuring gear. Then read the following aloud:\r\n\r\n[section:dialogue-box] The facade of the Bureau of Civic Relics boasts enormous columns and elegant archways hewn from marble. Cosmopolitan visitors bustle about the entrance, including some clad in sleek formalwear.[/section]\r\n\r\nThe Bureau is open to the public today; only the @[Gemstone Wing](landmark:7fae5c58-a5fa-4327-8b94-7f538ece2377) on the second floor is closed for the ticketed gala. The @[Eye of Anub-Ka](item:5594fa45-5159-41d5-b743-2a982466c629) is ensconced in the Gemstone Wing.\r\n\r\n[h2]Scouting the Bureau[/h2]\r\n\r\nThe characters can explore the public areas of the Bureau while it's open. The entire Bureau is public except for its offices",
